  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a world where the supernatural is natural. <strong><i>I</i></strong>n this single-player, first-person, survival, horror game where <strong><i>s</i></strong>pirits and people alike have existed together, for better or worse, since the dawn of man. Though, most seem to have forgotten what spirits and creatures lie just beyond the shadows. Th<strong><i>e</i></strong>ir presence only remembered through folklore and stories passed down through the g<strong><i>e</i></strong>nerations. Folklore that Jordan has heard since childhood. Stories the<strong><i>y</i></strong> never really believed t<strong><i>o</i></strong> be true....<strong><i>u</i></strong>ntil now. Follow Grandpa's instructions, light all the fires, and Jordan just might make it out alive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Interactive and immersive gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Open world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Horrifying enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Story driven<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840440/extras/91fe478b18bb23b876efcbbd1addf81b.avif?t=1729218160\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840440/extras_big/91fe478b18bb23b876efcbbd1addf81b.avif?t=1729218160 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
